2026-05-13T19:06:03.9047188Z 12    <!--
2026-05-13T19:06:03.9048004Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-13T19:06:03.9049112Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
